%h1 You're Invited To Collaborate

%p

  #{h(@invitation.sender_name)} has invited you to collaborate on a huddle 
  titled 
  %q #{h(@invitation.tree_title)}.
  To begin collaborating, click on the button below.

  - form_for(@invitation) do |f|
    = f.error_messages
    %p(style="text-align: center")
      = f.submit("Accept")